{
  "title": "Savory Malaysian Chicken Satay",
  "description": "A delicious and healthy Malaysian dish featuring chicken satay with a yeasty and molten flavor, perfect for a date night, made with extra virgin olive oil and bonito-shave, and Whole30-friendly.",
  "cuisine": "Malaysian",
  "diet": [
    "Whole30",
